parameters: $gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuWoEx.I don’t think we should wander until our tasks are complete.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrBaEx.I’m sorry, but Friday services have been canceled due to low attendance.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrEx.My name is 1Hero. I’m from the criminal investigations department.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrFrEx.Welcome, 1Hero. I’m Father Brian Solomon. I’m the new priest here at Eve Cathedral.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrFrOp.I honestly didn’t expect to see you here so soon.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaCl.Well… I didn’t… I mean… I had some time this afternoon.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.Let me ask… How do you know that girl who just left?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrFlOp.I doubt she has anything to do with what we’ve been hearing at night.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuWoEx.Someone has been rummaging through the church.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrBaEx.The noise seems to be coming from the storage room, but we’ve not seen anything.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.I can see you’re concerned with the noises, but don’t you think it’s likely an animal?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrBaEx.You’ll have to excuse Sister Judy. We’ve been through a lot since the death of Father Zephaniah.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuWoEx.I’m sorry. But it’s just that we’re alone here…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuBaEx.Father Solomon and I have been trying to get this church back on its feet.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaOp.If you don’t mind me asking... What happened?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrBaEx.To put it bluntly… Father Zephaniah was a loon.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrBaEx.The church was bleeding members long before I got here.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaDe.The second coming? As in the return of your savior?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrFlOp.I take it you’re not a religious man.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFlEx.Sorry, Father. Been skipping Sunday school for a long time now.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrBaEx.Zephaniah had an extremist view that drove away members.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuWoEx.I didn’t know Father Zephaniah that well. I only recently moved here after my previous church was destroyed.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaOp.Sounds like you’ve been through a lot.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuSaOp.It’s been a long time since I’ve felt at home.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrBaEx.With just the two of us here, Judy’s afraid it’s attracting attention from thieves.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrFlEx.I suspect you might just find the thief has four legs.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrFlOp.Show him around, Sister. Make him feel at home.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuFrEx.If you’ll follow me, I’ll show you our storage room…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuWoEx.It’s where we believe the noises came from.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoClNo1.Hell yeah, you are! What the hell are you?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ArShCl.How is this possible? I can’t be here… I never went to Limbo.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoCl.What are you talking about? Where are you from?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ArFrEx.I am from the Empyrean, little one.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ArFrOp.My name is Arianna. What is your name?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ArHaOp.Hello, 1Hero. I am here to assist you.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ArBaDe.I thought I had more time to prepare.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ArWoCl.There is dirt everywhere. Who is in charge of cleaning this place?...");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ArSaOp.Oh, you poor Earthling. You must not be familiar with cleanliness.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ArFrEx.In my world, we do something called... cleaning.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ArHaOp.Great! Then let’s clean this hideous place up.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFlEx.If you think this place is bad, then you’re going to hate the rest of the city.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoOp.How the hell are you supposed to assist me?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ArFrEx.I am the deliverer of God’s will.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaDe.This seems crazy… But so is a sexy babe with anatomically correct bird wings.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ArShOp.I’m a sexy babe? What does that mean?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.Okay. If you know the future, then tell me… What is God’s will?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ArFrEx.Today you’re going to visit Wilkes Mansion… Oh! And Heather is going to hand over to you a new home…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ArFrEx.Well… Everything that the supreme being has laid out for me to see.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.Okay… Then tell me. Am I going to solve the Wilkes murder case?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ArWoEx.I only know it when the time is right. Unless the maker guides me, I am in the dark.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ArFrEx.My powers only work through His almighty guidance.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrWoOp.Are you okay, 1Hero? Who are you talking to?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrBaEx.Did you find anything in the storage room?...");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrFlEx.Perhaps the paw prints of a mischievous cat?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrEx.Yeah, paw prints. I think you have a cat on the loose.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrOp.Everything is sorted. I think I helped to put her mind at ease.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrSaOp.I’m sorry we had to bother you.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrOp.It’s no trouble at all. I’m glad I was able to help.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrBaEx.Sounds like quite the storm outside. Care to stay for a bit?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrOp.I actually have to run. I have another case I’m investigating.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrOp.It’s been a pleasure to meet you, Father Solomon.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrHaOp.Give us a few months. We’ll have this place hoppin’ by Christmas.");
$gameVariables.setValue(25, "Storm is passing. Meet me at the house. I’m so proud of you!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoOp.Shit… Do I have time to go to the house and still make it to the Wilkes Mansion before Melissa leaves?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ArHaEx.You have plenty of time to do both.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaDe.So… I can go to the house first?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.But what if I’m late? Can I go to the mansion first and still make it to the home without keeping Heather waiting?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ArFrEx.Sometimes the order of things doesn’t matter, as long as you follow His will.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ArFrEx^.Your journey is just beginning, 1Hero. But you still have much to learn.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ArHaEx^.To start, let’s open your inventory and select your phone.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ChFrOp.I hope you solve your case, 1Hero. I believe in you.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrOp.Thanks, Chloe. And if I can help you in any way, let me know.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrFrEx.Please don’t wander the church. If you want, you can go into the chapel.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuWoEx.Please don’t wander the church. Father Soloman will get upset.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrFrEx.Please don’t wander the church. If you want, you can go into the chapel.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuWoEx.Please don’t wander the church. Father Soloman will get upset.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrFrEx.Please don’t wander the church. If you want, you can go into the chapel.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuWoEx.Please don’t wander the church. Father Soloman will get upset.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrFrOp.If you’re looking for Sister Judy, she’s on the other side of the building.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrBaOp.It’s getting late, 1Hero. Do you need something?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrFrEx.Please don’t wander the church. If you want, you can go into the chapel.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuWoEx.Please don’t wander the church. Father Soloman will get upset.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrFrOp.If you’re looking for Sister Judy, she’s on the other side of the building.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrBaOp.It’s getting late, 1Hero. Do you need something?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuBaEx.Oh, yes. She is praying in the chapel. She looked distraught.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoCl.Oh, uhh. I just put her in an awkward situation.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdBaDe.I need to leave this city... But not now.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaOp.I can see something on that shelf. But I can’t jump high enough to reach it.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuWoEx.Please help us with the broken rigging cable. The chapel is a dangerous place with a swinging chandelier.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrFrOp.If you’re looking for Sister Judy, she’s on the west side of the building.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrBaOp.It’s getting late, 1Hero. Do you need something?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrFrOp.If you’re looking for Sister Judy, she’s on the west side of the building.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrBaOp.It’s getting late, 1Hero. Do you need something?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrFrOp.If you’re looking for Sister Judy, she’s on the west side of the building.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrBaOp.It’s getting late, 1Hero. Do you need something?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuFrEx.Father Solomon is away, shopping. I am watching the church while he is away.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuFrOp.Do you need to investigate anything here?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrOp.Nothing planned. But you never know where a clue might pop up.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrBaEx.I’ll check the west end. But she may have gone outside.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrBaEx.I’m the one who does the shopping. Judy prefers to stay at the church…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ChWoOp.What are we going to do now? Is Sister Judy safe?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrFrEx.I won't leave her side. I’ll stay here in the church with her.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuFrOp.Thank you, Father Solomon. You’ve been so kind to me.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrEx.I’ll get to the bottom of this. When I’m finished, Madalyn will be behind bars.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrFlOp.Sounds to me like that won’t hold her.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ChWoEx.Can you do an exorcism spell on her, Father?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrHaOpNo3.Haha. Oh, Chloe. It’s not that simple.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrFlEx.But if she fears us, she’ll keep her distance from me.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrHaEx.A true demon is no match for the power of God.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuFrOp.I feel safe with you, Father. You have not let me down.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ChFrOp.I’ll stay with you too, Sister Judy…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ChFrEx.At least until it’s time for bed.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuFrEx.Come on, Chloe. Let us speak alone, in my bedroom.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrBaDe.Sister Judy has told me stories of her time at Saint Dame University…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrWoOp.But I never imagined that evil woman being an actual demon.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.I would have thought that sounded crazy… But I’ve seen so much now. I believe it’s true.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrFlEx.You're in deeper than you expected, I’m sure.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrFrEx.When it comes to the spiritual, I can help you.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrFrOp.Come to me whenever you need help.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrFlDe.You are certainly popular with the ladies.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrBaDe.1Hero… Sister Judy told me what happened.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuWoEx^.We must find a relic to save Erica!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ArWoEx.And Lilith plans to attack… So we must also find the amulets.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoEx.We have to hurry… Lillian has access to Ella’s Lustagram account.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "TaWoEx^.Shit… It means she’s going to post the Toma online.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuWoCl^.But we can’t harm Lilith… She’s the one who can bring back Erica.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HrWoDe.Then you better hurry up, because we can’t risk the fate of the world to save one person.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoOp.We don’t even know what the hell these amulets will do to her.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrBaDe.That’s true… Even if we had them, I don’t know how to use them.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "TaFlDe^.Sounds like more reading is in store.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuWoCl^.You don’t know where he would have kept holy relics?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrFlEx.This place has a lot of junk lying around. Zephaniah was not the most organized priest…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrBaDe.I’m sure most of the stuff you’ll find here is fake.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuWoCl^.But we’re a Catholic church. Surely we have genuine relics.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "TaBaDe^.I fail to see how a relic is going to bring back Erica.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuWoEx^.Erica will have to put it inside of her… body.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoEx.It’s Lilith’s plan… But it makes sense when you think about it.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "TaFlEx^.No need to sell me. I like the idea.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrWoOp.How the hell is this supposed to work?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrEx.Well… God sends Erica to Hell… Lillian gives Erica her body back… She walks out of the rift a free woman.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrBaDe.Hence why we can’t close the rift and banish Lilith until Erica is back here alive.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "TaFlEx^.No biggie. Save Erica, then kill Lillian. Easy.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DiBaDe^.Then you better find the relic soon.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "TaBaEx^.Dad and I will figure out how to fuck Lilith up with the amulets.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuWoEx^.I can help you search, but how will we know if the relic is genuine?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrBaEx.I know we’re all running on fumes, but let’s stay focused. We all know what needs to be done.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HrBaEx.We can’t trust Lilith. If we know how to take out Lilith, we need to do it.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DiBaEx^.We’ll start the search for the amulets.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaDe.The cops are all over the mansion.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrBaEx.I’ll give you a description of the amulets so you know what to look for.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuWoOp^.I guess it’s up to us to find that relic.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ArBaEx.A true holy relic causes pain to demons that are scheming against God.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ArWoEx.Not exactly… The line between angel and demon is shaded with gray.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ArWoEx.I must approach the darkness… As I get closer, I will feel pain… Then I will sense the source of the pain.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ArBaEx.Don’t worry about that. It’s something I have to figure out.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ArBaEx.Everyone, split up. Bring anything you think might be a holy relic to me… I will test it.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuWoEx.Father told me what he saw. You are brave to venture into those woods at night.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HnAnDe.For a place so big, it sure is short on fun stuff to do.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrEx.Why don’t you go to the woods?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HnShCl.Did you run over here in the rain!?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HnAnDe.I ain’t walking home. Where is Ma?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrBaEx.Sister Judy is safe. Perhaps I should go with you.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.Stay here with Judy. If I see anything, I’ll come back for you.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrOp.I can use my container to collect some of this holy water.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaOp.If I had a container I could collect some of this holy water.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaDe.What if I used an unholy container to collect holy water?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuWoCl.I never suspected I would see your former wife. This is very shocking.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "NeAnDe.I guess our paths truly did diverge.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ChWoOp>.I don’t get it. Why did you come back to him?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "NeAnEx.I’m not here for Brian. I have my own reasons for coming to North Santiva.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrAnDe^.Reasons that involve running around the forest in the dark?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "NeAnEx.If you must know, yes! And it’s none of your business.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McShCl.Wait… So is Brian the father of Tasha?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "NeWoCl.Hey now… Let’s not jump to any conclusions.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "NeAnEx.Everybody needs to start minding their own business.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrAnDe^.Are you being full of shit, Nellie?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "NeAnDe.I don’t know what you’re talking about.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuHaEx.Perhaps you would feel better after taking a warm shower.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuFrEx.But you’ve gotten all wet and dirty. Surely you’d feel better if you cleaned up.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ChShCl>.This is crazy. Father Solomon might be a father… I mean… A real father.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McShOp.I can’t believe you’re connected to Nellie.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrFlEx.That’s the woman, 1Hero. That’s the old ball and chain.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrBaDe.Although, we didn’t have a typical relationship.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ChWoOp.That doesn’t look like the type of woman I’d have imagine you being with.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrFlEx.You didn’t know me twenty years ago.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ChFrOp.Well, at least we found out it wasn’t Madalyn.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrAnDe.I’d almost rather have seen a demon.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrEx.Come on, Father. She can’t be that bad.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrFlEx.Look at what she did to me.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McHaOpNo3.Haha. Maybe you owe her some thanks.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrFrEx.Thanks for trying to help, you two.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuFrEx.1Hero, give me your clothes and you can stay in my room while they dry.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrFrEx.Come on, Chloe. I’ll walk you home while 1Hero cleans up.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrBaEx.1Hero, don’t let her leave until I get back. I’m not done with her.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McAnDe.Shit. I’m not going to try and stop her.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuWoEx.1Hero… I heard you in the bathroom.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFlEx.I don’t fight the desire, Sister Judy.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoCl.I’m sorry. I won’t do it again.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuWoEx.I mean… How did you do it?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoEx.Uhh. I couldn’t stop her… She left.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrAnEx.She was supposed to be out of my life.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaDe.Is it possible she had your child?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrBaEx.It’s exactly what Nellie would have done.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuWoCl.You have a daughter here in North Santiva? I can’t believe it.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrAnDe.No… It can’t be. She’s messing with my head.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrAnDe.That woman didn’t have my kid. It can’t be true.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoEx.Now’s probably not a good time to talk to Father Solomon.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuSaOp.It’s getting late. Perhaps I should go to bed.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrEx.I’ll leave you alone, Judy. I should get going.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrEx.Goodbye, Judy. I’ll come visit again soon.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeBaOp>.It’s quite a beautiful church you have here.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeFlDe>.Catholicism isn’t quite my religion of choice.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuWoEx.He’s away. We have a roof repair that we’re working on.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeBaOp>.Can we see Father Zephaniah’s old quarters?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuWoEx.I’m afraid that is where Father Solomon sleeps now, and he locks it while he is away.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeBaEx>.In the meantime, can we check the other areas?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuFrOp.Of course. And if there’s anything you need from me, please do ask.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuFrEx.Yes, and there is a storage area and attic access there as well.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeBaEx>.1Hero, let’s start searching. We’re looking for a prescription bottle.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuWoCl.Oh, my. Something like that may have been thrown away.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeBaOp>.The police would have seized it when they came. Hopefully, if it’s here, it has remained overlooked.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.If I had to guess, Madalyn’s murder spree may have taken Father Zephaniah.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuWoCl.My goodness! It’s so hard to believe that I have been close to such a woman.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuSaCl.I do hope that you’re able to find what you need.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuBaEx.If you need me, I’ll be checking on our leak. It seems to have gotten worse.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrEx.Hopefully Father Solomon can fix it before it starts to rain.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuSaCl.I don’t have high hopes. It’s been leaking for weeks.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ChFlEx.Carol and Mom are messing with that truck of hers. I didn’t want to hang around and hear their gossip talk.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.My boss has me investigating another crime.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.Seems the old priest may have been murdered by Madalyn.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ChWoClNo1.No way! Where is Judy? Is she safe?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrEx.She’s fine. She’s upstairs checking on a leak.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ChFrEx.Thanks. I’m going to go talk to her.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BoAnEx^.Where the hell were you hiding? We looked everywhere.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McAnDe.I need to talk to the commissioner.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.Duncan’s gone. He got what he wanted.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McAnEx.Kimura told me to keep an eye on Duncan. I’m telling you where to look.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McSaOp.I’m sorry about all of this, Father Solomon.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrBaEx.Sounds like they would have shown up no matter what. But I still have no idea what Zephaniah was up to, and what those amulets mean.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaOp.Judy mentioned that amulets are for protection.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrBaDe.That’s true. But protection from evil is not something I would imagine a demon needs.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaOp.Do you think Zephaniah was planning to use the amulet against Madalyn?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrBaOp.Zephaniah is dead. Not sure what that plan would have been.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrBaEx.I told them I’d come check on you and then they went home. Everyone was very worried.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoEx.Don’t tell them, but things got pretty hairy.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaDe.I’ve got a bone to pick with the commissioner.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrBaEx.Good luck, 1Hero. I’ve got my own problems with Nellie I need to sort out.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrBaDe.She has some good qualities, but be careful around her.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeBaEx.We have some information on Madalyn Rose, the woman who was reported seen near your church.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.She may have been scouting this area for quite some time.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeBaOp.DNA from a hair sample was retrieved from the body of Father Zephaniah…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeBaEx.The cause of death was listed as a heart attack, but with this new information, we’d like to locate his belongings.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrBaEx.The police took everything. There’s not really anything left.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.Zephaniah took heart meds, and we don’t have them.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeBaEx.We suspect that they were never found and might still be hidden somewhere out of sight.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrBaEx.I can show you my bedroom. It was the place where Father Zephaniah’s belongings were kept.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ChWoEx.Uhh, guys. We have a big problem.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrBaEx.If there was anything left behind from Father Zephaniah’s time here, it would now be in the attic.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeBaEx.Looks like the weather is letting up. I’m heading home.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaDe.How are we going to get into the safe?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeBaEx.We have people at the station that can handle that sort of thing.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.But there could be a code laying around. We could at least look.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeBaEx.Thank you, Father Solomon, for letting us search for Zephaniah’s belongings.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrWoDe^.I’ll admit Madalyn scares me. I wish I knew what she wanted.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeBaEx.I can see about having some officers posted outside.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeBaEx.We’ll have to show there is a possible danger…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeBaDe.Let’s wait and see what’s in that safe.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ChFrEx>.Come on, Sister Judy. I’m excited to show you my place.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuHaOp.It will be exciting to spend a night away.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrFlEx.Just bring her back in one piece.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuHaAgNo3.Haha. You are so funny, Father Solomon.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrBaEx.If there was anything left behind from Father Zephaniah’s time here, it would now be in the attic.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ChBaEx.The police officer is not very friendly.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFlEx.He’s a pain in the ass for sure, but he’ll keep you safe.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrEx.Of course, Sister Judy. We need to clean that room of yours.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ChWoEx.It’s pretty bad, 1Hero… It smells like mold.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuSaCl.I hope the bed is not ruined. We can’t afford to be buying new beds with our low attendance.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuHaOp.I feel very refreshed today. I slept so well last night.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaDe.Looks like Melissa is calling. I bet she found something.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeBaOp.Checking the autopsy reports, Zephaniah’s potassium levels were elevated…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeBaEx.Not fatal for a younger man, but if someone knew he had a condition, a dose this high would cause heart failure.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeAnEx.That would mean Madalyn knew him personally… At least close enough to know his medical history.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McAnEx.I’m at the church… looking for clues.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeBaOp.I’m close by. I will be there soon.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.Hi, Father Solomon… Detective Bhatt is on her way over.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.Zephaniah was poisoned… and I think Madalyn did it.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.If it’s true, that means she’s killed at least two priests in the last couple years.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrBaDe.How can a demon kill a priest? There are many ways for holy men to ward off demons.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaDe.Maybe she manipulated them to let their guards down…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.I have a journal… It was in the safe.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrEx.Maybe it can shed some light on their potential relationship.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.Detective Bhatt is going to want to take it as evidence.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrFlEx.No offense, but I don’t trust the police with matters of theology.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrEx.We have some time. Let’s look at it together.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeBaEx.Hello, Father Solomon. I’m sorry to be the bearer of bad news…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeBaOp.I think Father Zephaniah could have been poisoned.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeBaEx.We don’t know that yet… But I think we can justify a police watch, if you feel unsafe.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeBaDe.I am aware that 1Hero found it in the safe.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrBaEx.If you don’t mind, I’d like to keep it and read through it…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrFrEx.Perhaps there are answers that I’d be able to find.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeBaEx.We’d sure like to have it as evidence. We have investigators that can comb over it.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrBaEx.Due to our shared religious beliefs, I think I’d be able to make better use of the journal.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeBaDe.It’s not necessary we take it. We have what we need to draw connections between him and Madalyn…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeBaEx.If you want to keep it, I think we can let that slide.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeBaEx.However, we need more evidence. I hope you don’t mind us being here.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrFrEx.Not at all. Feel free to look around.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ChWoCl.Uhh… 1Hero. You may want to come look at this.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ChWoEx.We found something under Sister Judy’s rug.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "TaFlEx^.We’re going to go kick Madalyn’s ass.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoEx.Erica… You should stay here with Sister Judy.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ErWoCl.You’re really going back to the mansion?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoEx.I found Madalyn… and she has Kimberly.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrBaEx.I will help him find the girl. But Lillian wants you for the ritual, Erica.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrBaEx.Erica is a descendant of a Casula witch… She is needed to put the Toma back together.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DiBaDe^.And we still are not sure what it does…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrBaEx.Erica… You and Judy will be here with Detective Bhatt.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ErBaEx.She was naked… It was either this or the nun uniform.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrBaEx.If you weren’t there, it’s hard to describe.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "TaFrEx^.It looked like a metal album cover.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeBaDe^.I’m sure there’s a rational explanation for all of this.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ErBaOp.Should we get back to our studies?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "KiWoOp^.Shit! I need to tell Paul I’m okay. He’s probably worried sick.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeBaEx^.1Hero and I will come with you.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrBaEx.Careful, 1Hero. You’ve been exposed to powers that even I can’t comprehend.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrBaDe.She was clearly affected by seeing the cross… but I have a feeling that we’ve not seen the last of her.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeBaEx^.Come on, 1Hero. Let’s get Kimberly back to her office.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrFrEx.We’ve got things under control. I feel safer knowing we’re being looked after.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BoFlEx.Why don’t you spend the night, I’m headed over to the mansion.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BoAnEx.I’d send another unit, but it’s Friday night.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BoBaEx.Someone was spotted snooping around… I’m not taking any chances. I need to get over there.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.Stay here and make sure no one comes into the church. I’ll go to the mansion.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BoFlDe.Looking to score some points with the Wilkes girl?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BoAnEx.Don’t wait around. Get over there and check it out.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BoAnEx.Go to the mansion and make sure my officer is okay.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BoAnDe.Are all these girls supposed to be here? I’m not a babysitter.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BoAnDe.What a horrible way to spend a weekend. You owe me, 1Hero.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrBaDe.Officer Rinaldi was in a hurry to leave. Is everything okay?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.The commissioner must feel there’s a bigger threat at the Wilkes mansion, but don’t worry, an officer will be here Monday.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McSaEx.Sorry, Father. But I can help out until we can get more help.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "NeAnOp^.God Damn, I didn’t think that cop would ever leave.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrAnDe.You owe me an explanation. What are you doing here?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrAnDe.You’re living under my church and running around the woods. Why are you tormenting me?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "NeAnDe^.There’s a monster harassing us and I think you might know how to stop it.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoEx.She’s talking about Madalyn Rose… The half demon.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "NeAnEx^.She appeared out of thin air and kidnapped me… and she made a hell of a mess in our hideout.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.She’s telling the truth. I was there…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoEx.Madalyn appeared and I used the holy water on her but after a few minutes she must have gained her powers back because she vanished.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "NeAnEx^.She’s fucking up our shit. You have to help us stop her.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrAnDe.Watch your damn mouth, woman. You’re in a church.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "NeAnEx^.You can’t turn me away this time, Brian. I need you.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrAnDe.I gave you a chance. You took a different road.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "NeAnEx^.Enough about the past. Are you not a man of God? If she’s a demon, this is your problem as much as it is mine.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrBaDe.If she’s demon possessed, I can cast it back to hell… But only if she’s human on the inside.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaOp.Have you heard of a shell being?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.A… vessel specifically made for demon possession.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrBaDe.That shouldn’t be possible. Where did you hear about that?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "NeAnEx^.This isn’t going anywhere. Can’t you use holy water and some stupid prayer?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrAnDe.Are you hiding something from me, Nellie?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "NeAnDe^.I don’t know what you’re talking about… It’s either kill the monster or give her what she wants.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaOp.Do you think Father Zephaniah might have written about them?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrBaDe.Why would he be a part of this?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoCl.I… I don’t know if I should say.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.It was here, in the hidden basement.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrBaDe.So you think it belonged to Zephaniah?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "NeFrEx^.So we only need to find one more.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McAnDe.I’m not giving it to Madalyn. We don’t even know what it is?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "NeAnEx^.I didn’t sign up for this. Dealing with a crazy gang leader is one thing, but a demon? I’m just about to call it quits.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrAnDe.If you’re hanging out with gang leaders then I don’t want you hanging out around me.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrEx.Trust her Father Solomon. She has her reasons.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrWoEx.If a demon wants it, it can’t be good.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.I’d give it to you, but if bad people are looking for it, I don’t think it would be wise to keep it at the church.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrBaOp.Keep it, 1Hero. I’ll look into this and see what I can figure out.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrAnOp.I think you know exactly what I’m getting at.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrAnExNo1.Gad damn it, woman! No cussing in the church!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuWoCl.Oh, I’m sorry to interrupt. I didn’t know we had company.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrAnEx>.Come on Nellie. Let’s talk in my bedroom.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuWoCl.What’s going on? Where is Officer Bobby?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrEx.He had to leave, but I’m here to make sure everything is okay.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.Madalyn is looking for two amulets… But we don’t know why.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuBaEx.That’s what I always thought amulets were for… Protection from demons.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaDe.I doubt Madalyn needs protection from demons.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ChFrOp^.Come to prepare for church tomorrow with Judy and I, 1Hero?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrEx.Oh, no. I’m here because Officer Rinaldi left.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuBaEx.Nellie came too… She’s talking to Father.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrEx.I’ll stick around for a bit. How’s Heather doing?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ChSaEx^.I can’t get her to talk to me. She insists everything is fine.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuFrEx.She should have come with you. Perhaps she needs the Lord.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrOp.Just what kind of preparation do you need to do, Sister?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ChFrEx^.She insisted I come. She must be excited about something.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuFrCl.I just need some advice on… bible verses.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuHaEx.The time is getting away from us, perhaps we should go into the chapel.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuFrOp.Thank you for keeping guard, 1Hero. Let us know if you see anything suspicious.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.Andrea would kill me if she knew, but we’re going back to the mansion to save Kimberly.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DiAnEx^.He’s better off with us than any dimwit on your force.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "NeBaEx.Come on. Duncan’s waiting. We have to go.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "NeBaEx.I’ll sneak everyone into the basement… 1Hero, I’ll meet you there and bring you to Duncan.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ErFrOp.Nice to see you again, Miss Bhatt.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuHaEx^.Would you like a tour of the church?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ErFrEx.Come on. Let’s go back to the library.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.Don’t let them out of your sight. There’s a cult looking to kidnap Erica… and they probably know she’s here.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeWoDe.I don’t like the sound of that.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.She’s getting ready. When does church start?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrSaDe.One hour… I just pray that people show up.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrFrEx.It’s been quiet without Judy around. But it does seem attendance is up a bit.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrHaOp.I better get going. Thanks for stopping by to protect us.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoEx.Not sure if she’s going to make it. She was still in her underwear when I left.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "TaHaAg.I can’t wait to kick some ass.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DuFlEx.My name is Duncan Helmer. I was an acquaintance of Father Zephaniah.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DuFlDe.Let’s just say… He knew my grandma.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrBaDe>.Well… I’m sorry for your loss. I personally did not know him very well.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DuAnDe.Of course. It was very hard for our whole family.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DuFlEx.Don’t mind my acquaintance. She’s… not used to church.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrAnDe>.So, what do you want from me?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DuBaEx.My grandmother gave Father Zephaniah a family heirloom, and now that the old man has kicked the bucket… We want it back.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DuBaEx.It’s gold with a turquoise gem in the middle.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DuBaEx.Think about it, Father. We’re going to need it back.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrBaEx>.Sorry. I’ve been through all of Zephaniah’s belongings. Nothing rings a bell.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DuFlBe.If you don’t mind. Can we take a look around?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrAnDe>.Knock yourself out. You won’t find anything.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrBaEx.That amulet you have… They are looking for it.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoOp.We need to get everyone out of here.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoEx.Judy! Chloe! You two need to leave.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrBaOp.I’ll take them away from here. What are you going to do?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoEx.Duncan is here with his henchmen. You all need to leave…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaOp.Go to my place. It’s close by…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.I’ll leave and meet you back at my house as soon as more officers arrive.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrAnEx.Church is over. We’re going to 1Hero’s house.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrBaEx.Come on. We can’t linger. Let’s get you ladies out of here.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.I… I’m calling for backup. Don’t worry about me.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoCl^.Shit… I need to call Andrea. She needs to know about this first.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoEx.He’s looking for something. Everyone else left, but him and his henchmen are rummaging around the place.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdAnEx.Follow him! Don’t let him out of your sight.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoCl.I’m unarmed. Shouldn’t I call for backup?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdAnEx.I’ll deal with that. Get your eyes on Duncan.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoCl^.What the hell? What am I trying to find?... and where is Nellie?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrAnDe.I have no idea where your mother is.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "TaSaDe^.Henry is gone… And now Diana… I don’t know what to do.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "TaAnDe^.What the hell? She needs to tell me what’s going on.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrAnEx.Don’t count on your mother, Tasha. I learned that the hard way.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrBaEx.Listen… I’m studying something… But you can stay.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ErBaOp^.Do you need help with the Casula language?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrBaEx.I do. There’s something going on that’s brought a demonic presence to North Santiva…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrBaDe.I suspect it has something to do with the Toma Leolo.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "TaFlEx^.You know… I happen to have some experience with Casula rituals myself.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "TaFlEx^.Oh yeah… I’ve been in the depths of some crazy magic temples.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "TaSaEx^.I need to find Diana and Henry.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.Duncan is looking for an amulet… by order of Madalyn.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaDe.If we can find Madalyn, we can find Duncan.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrBaEx.You're not just dealing with Earthly criminals. You’re dealing with demonic magic.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HnAnEx^.I told ya! I’m bored and I want to go home!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeFrEx.No one’s forcing you to be here.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HnSaOp^.But I also want to have fun with the gang!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ErHaOp^.Nice to see you again, Miss Heather.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ChFlEx>.Seems like your wish is coming true, Hannah. More people for you to annoy.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrBaOp.We better get back to our studies.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HnHaEx^.Come on, Ella. You can come with me to the farm. We can play with my new pet goat!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeFlOp.Sounds like you two have some fun ahead of you.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ElFrOp.I guess a farm is as safe a place as any.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFlOp.Don’t worry. I think you can handle Hannah.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.Heather… The case I was working on… We finished it today.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McSaEx.I might not get my job back as a detective.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeWoCl.Get your job back? What do you mean?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McSaEx.Yeah… She recorded Ella and me having sex for the world to see.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeFrEx.Do the right thing and everything will work out.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeFrOp.If you ever need my help, let me know.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeFrEx.It seems Chloe will be busy tonight with Judy. I should head home and clean up a bit.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaDe.Duncan’s going to know where to find you.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrBaOp.Any way to bring back the police presence?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McAnDe.The commissioner is going to have to make a move, undercover operation be damned.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HrAnDe>.He can only be alive because she wants him alive. There’s no other reason for it.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DiAnDe^.Duncan has too much influence… We should have known this would be impossible.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ErWoOp.What’s going to happen to Lillian?... She’s going to be caught.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaDe.She’s probably hiding inside the rift… I don’t know if Duncan can chase her there.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrBaEx.That rift leads to hell. He’d be wise to not chase her.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DiBaEx^.If Duncan comes looking for the priest, we can be here to intercept him.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.Let me get with the commissioner. I’ll fix this.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ErWoOp.It’s very late. I should get back home.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoEx.Lillian wants you, Erica. Stay away from the mansion.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ErFrEx.I’ll stop by later. We can figure this out.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HrBaDe>.What’s going on? What are you studying?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaOp.Father Solomon, how are you holding up?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrBaEx.Nothing out of the ordinary. Have you spoken with the commissioner?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.She’s heading here to meet with you personally.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.I’ll speak with her this morning and let you know the plan.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrBaDe.Being in such close proximity to a mansion full of thieves makes me very uncomfortable…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrWoEx.But what really worries me is not having a full grasp on what Lillian wants.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoDe.Madalyn too… She thinks Sister Judy is trying to stop her.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrBaDe.A virgin servant of the Lord can be quite frightening to a woman like that.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrBaEx.The police can’t help us against the powers of evil… We need to take matters into our own hands.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrFlEx.We arm this place to the teeth.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrFlEx.Enough so no demon can enter here without seeing one… Let’s call it five.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrFlEx.And a good amount of holy water.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrBaEx.I’ll be in the library, studying. Bring them to me when you have them…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrFrEx.There may be some in storage. But if not, you may have to get creative.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrOp.You’ll be able to go home tonight. I’ll make sure everything’s okay.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ChSaOp.Ugh! I’m mortified that Mom saw us.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrOp.We were just having fun. It’s not a big deal.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrOp.You know, now that you’re in a human body, there are things you can do that you couldn’t before.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFlOp.Like what was about to happen between us before you left Erica’s body.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MlAnDeNo1.Keep your mind on God’s work, mister.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DiAnDe.I’m not too happy about hanging around here.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuWoCl.Thank the Lord that Father Brian wasn’t here… Hannah was buck naked!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ErWoOp.I hope we can figure this out soon.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ChBaDe.Something seemed funny about Carol and Mom.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrEx.Maybe these Casula books will finally give you the answers you need.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "NeBaDe^.Just what the hell are you planning to do?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrBaDe.I’m guessing we’ve not seen the last of that secret mansion basement.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuWoCl.Oh, dear. I hope all the danger is behind us.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "NeBaDe^.Do you expect me to sneak you into the mansion again?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrBaEx.Come on, Nellie. I’ll explain what we know.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrOp.Aren't you going to help them study?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuFlOp.Yet I can’t stop thinking about you.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HnHaEx^.Y'all want to go on an adventure?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuSaEx.I wanted to speak to you in my bedroom.");

$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrBaEx.Stay here with the girls. I’ll go with 1Hero to the rift.");

$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeBaEx^.I’m coming with you. I need to see this for myself.");

$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrEx.I will… Make sure Judy is safe.");

$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McSaEx.She’s… She is in the hands of Lillian now.");

$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HrFrEx.There’s hope. I believe we can defeat this evil.");

$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaDe.I don’t think we’re going anywhere tonight.");

$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrEx.This is Arianna… An angel from Heaven.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MlFrEx>.That’s right. I have come to you in the body of a demi-demon…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MlFrEx>.But I am here to guide you all to victory.");

$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.Our saving grace is that Lilith is selective… She won’t use the Toma without warning.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "TaBaDe.Do you think she’ll try to use the studio again?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.I think that ship has sailed, unless those demons know how to fix broadcast equipment.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrWoCl.How the hell would we stop that?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HnAnEx^.We have to bait her. It’s the only way.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HrBaDe.And how exactly would we do that?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrBaDe.Let’s say it’s true that they have powers… We don’t know how to use them.");

$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MlFrEx>.They won’t be destroyed… Lilith doesn’t have the power to destroy them.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.And she’s probably hiding them in or near the mansion.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrEx.I can help… If Bobby is convinced, he can convince his men to help.");

$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrFrEx.Even if we don’t know how they work, it could distract Lilith long enough for us to have another crack at the Toma.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrEx.It can keep a demon from teleporting.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrFrEx.We have a plan… But we need rest.");

$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HrFrEx.I’m living proof that people can come back from Limbo… I know we’ll succeed.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdBaDe.Not where I was expecting to sleep tonight. But I suppose it’s better than whatever Jon’s accommodations were.");

$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdBaDe.You know… I had an amulet, but I can’t seem to find it.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoOp.Who the hell is calling me from work at this hour?");

$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaOp.I told you. What did you see?");
